<p>
<note n="0810b02" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0810b02">久如者言久遠<choice cb:resp="#resp1"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>如是非朝夕也我如者謂以我真如之性諸法畢備也</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0807b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0807b01">言雖不捨一法寔不存一見</note>
<note n="0807b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0807b02">惡不善法云云謂現世於惡不善法發動於內尚有容貌改變之害況起身口業寧無後世之報耶</note>
<note n="0807b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0807b03">比智者如上所說皆比量之智也此句此總下文合觀</note>
<note n="0810b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b01">前破學道執空相者所破義淺狹單明生死之業故此破學道執法空者所破義深廣備明修淨之說故</note>
<note n="0810b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b02">久如者言久遠巳如是非朝夕也我如者謂以我真如之性諸法畢備也</note>
<note n="0810b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b03">喚水火來言呼取水而火來也此設言必無之事</note>
<note n="0810b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b04">觀心者言既觀心是平等之法身則應隨處平等</note>
<note n="0810b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b05">無方便慧縛有方便慧解此維摩語</note>
<note n="0810b06" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b06">通人以路築舍以基故反言以明相之不可離也</note>
<note n="0810b07" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b07">淨法身言法身具眾相但不可生執著見去推度耳</note>
<note n="0810b08" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0810b08">楞嚴經證上息心亦妄句亦各段俱此意</note>
<note n="0811b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0811b01">依然取捨者取離淨穢捨不離淨穢也脫有取捨豈真唯心</note>
<note n="0812b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0812b01">通篇大意云謂西方若係權說則華藏世界亦權也以至文殊普賢尼父顏淵皆權也如此等賢聖為寔有則西方亦寔有矣又觀長者論言華藏世界乃佛之寔報與世人所見華藏世界不同是華藏為寔有則西方亦寔有矣及靈幹願生華藏華藏可生則西方亦可生矣</note>
</p>
